  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Build a school for 400 vulnearble kids in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is constructing a Primary School as well as a vocational center to benefit over 400 vulnerable children in Mpigi District. The school will be registered with the Ministry of Education and Sports (MoES). Children will be provided with all round Education from Kindergarten up to primary seven and this will enable them to obtain a Uganda National Examinations Board (UNEB) certificate at the Center which qualifies them for vocational training.</narrative>
  </description>
